<!-- Stage 3 Quiz — Bootstrap Carousel -->
<div class="quiz-section">
  <h4 class="quiz-section_title">Check Your Understanding</h4>
  <p class="quiz-section_intro">See if you caught the key points from this stage.</p>

  <div id="quizCarouselS3" class="carousel slide quiz-carousel" data-bs-interval="false" data-bs-wrap="false" data-bs-touch="true" data-total="2">

    <!-- Indicators -->
    <div class="carousel-indicators quiz-dots">
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#quizCarouselS3" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="quiz-dot active" aria-current="true"></button>
      <button type="button" data-bs-target="#quizCarouselS3" data-bs-slide-to="1" class="quiz-dot"></button>
    </div>

    <div class="carousel-inner">

      <!-- Q1 -->
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <div class="quiz-card">
          <p class="quiz-card_count">Question 1 of 2</p>
          <p class="quiz-card_question">How many IVF cycles does the Ontario Fertility Program (OFP) fund per eligible patient?</p>
          <div class="quiz-card_options">
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">Unlimited</button>
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">Three</button>
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">Two</button>
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="true">One</button>
          </div>
          <div class="quiz-card_feedback quiz-card_feedback--correct">
            ✓ <strong>Correct.</strong> The Ontario government funds one IVF cycle per eligible patient per lifetime through the OFP. Medications and additional services like genetic testing are typically not covered.
          </div>
          <div class="quiz-card_feedback quiz-card_feedback--wrong">
            ✗ <strong>Not quite.</strong> The OFP covers one IVF cycle per eligible patient per lifetime. This is something many people are surprised to learn exists at all.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Q2 -->
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <div class="quiz-card">
          <p class="quiz-card_count">Question 2 of 2</p>
          <p class="quiz-card_question">Which statement about fertility treatment in Ontario is correct?</p>
          <div class="quiz-card_options">
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">IVF is the only fertility treatment available</button>
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="true">Your doctor may recommend IUI, medication-only cycles, or lifestyle changes depending on your diagnosis</button>
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">All fertility treatments are fully covered by OHIP</button>
            <button class="quiz-option" data-correct="false">You must complete 6 IUI cycles before being eligible for IVF</button>
          </div>
          <div class="quiz-card_feedback quiz-card_feedback--correct">
            ✓ <strong>Correct.</strong> Treatment is not one-size-fits-all. Depending on your diagnosis, your doctor may recommend options other than IVF, including IUI, medication-only cycles, or lifestyle changes.
          </div>
          <div class="quiz-card_feedback quiz-card_feedback--wrong">
            ✗ <strong>Not quite.</strong> IVF is not the only option. Depending on your diagnosis, your doctor may recommend IUI, medication-only cycles, or even lifestyle changes first. Treatment plans are personalized.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

